review_title: The colour is nice and vibrant
reviews: The colour is nice and vibrant. I like the soft texture. A few keys on the keyboard cover aren't sitting exactly over the keys. The top piece of the case doesn't quite fit over, it stays on but doesn't latch on (I have macbook pro 15"). Makes the laptop feel SO heavy, I was shocked.

review_title: Disappointed that I've only used it a handful of times ...
reviews: Disappointed that I've only used it a handful of times and it's stopped working with my USB to wall charger box which is the Apple brand.

review_title: It's a nice hat but there's too much fabric on the top
reviews: It's a nice hat but there's too much fabric on the top, it sticks up and looks funny. We're going to cut the top and sew it back to make it a normal size.

Good quality water bottle. Compared to my stainless steel water bottle I notice how quickly my water gets warm in this one. Even with ice cubes, they're gone soon after putting them in. The smaller hole for drinking is convenient but it doesn't come out as a smooth flow as I had read in other comments. Arrived on time, in new packaging. If you're looking for a standard water bottle, this may be it! Main reason I chose this one was for cute colours.

review_title: Perhaps I'm just sensitive but they did make me want ...
reviews: Perhaps I'm just sensitive but they did make me want to gag while I wore them. It was hard to keep them in for so long without them sliding around on my teeth because of saliva. When you take them out, you can see where it wasn't properly stuck to your teeth and where the bubbles were because some parts of your teeth are more white than others.

The tempered glass screen protector that came with it never adhered to my phone correctly so I was left with large spots on both top corners of my screen. The case itself isn't too bad, although easy to crack. It does make your phone nice and slim and looks well covered, although I do have scratches on the back of my phone now from dirt getting in. Overall, cheap quality and not very satisfied. I've since changed to a commuter otterbox and love it.

review_title: Fits nicely, looks great and is of good quality
reviews: I bought this as a gift for my boyfriend and he loves it! Fits nicely, looks great and is of good quality. I would recommend for fellow john deere lovers!
